node.text:
Josh Barnett's: Bloodsport III
Minoru Suzuki vs Chris Dickinson is coming to Bloodsport.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by "𝕿𝖍𝖊 𝖂𝖆𝖗𝖒𝖆𝖘𝖙𝖊𝖗" Josh Barnett in Ukrainian Art Center Los Angeles with @suzuki.d.minoru, @fitetv, @gamechangerwrestling, and @joshbarnettbloodsport. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
My brother in Gotch-ism. Fellow "King of Pancrase", @suzuki.d.minoru is coming back to the hardest hitting event in professional wrestling. 

This is where you will see Suzuki-san thrive above all others. This, is Josh Barnett's: Bloodsport

Tix on Sale on Eventbrite, streaming live October 22nd on @fitetv

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by "𝕿𝖍𝖊 𝖂𝖆𝖗𝖒𝖆𝖘𝖙𝖊𝖗" Josh Barnett in Ukrainian Art Center Los Angeles with @kellywrestling, @fitetv, @gamechangerwrestling, and @joshbarnettbloodsport. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
Ever since competing at Josh Barnett's: Bloodsport 3, @kellywrestling has been telling me how much she wants to get back in this ring and go to war with someone.

Welcome back Killer Kelly. We're glad to have you.

Streaming LIVE on @FiteTV, October 22nd! Tix on Eventbrite to watch live in LA.

node.text:
Our first announced athlete for Josh Barnett's: Bloodsport 7 - Marina Shafir. (@marinashafir)
..
This Judo, Catch Wrestling, and MMA wrestler is transitioning from competing in NXT back to her roots.
.
Watch her in action October 22nd, streaming live only on @fitetv from the Ukrainian Cultural Center in Los Angeles.
.
@joshbarnettbloodsport @gamechangerwrestling

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by "𝕿𝖍𝖊 𝖂𝖆𝖗𝖒𝖆𝖘𝖙𝖊𝖗" Josh Barnett on September 15, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and people standing.

node.text:
If you didn't know.
.
If you're new to me and Pro Wrestling.
.
This is who I roll with. These are the types of people that brought me in the biz. These are who specifically picked me to stand with them.
.
People like Sayama (Tiger Mask) who has taken me aside to have deep discussions on Martial Arts and Wrestling.
.
Fujinami (Who watched me roll in the NJPW ring my first trip to wrestle and told me it reminded him of watching Gotch)
.
Inoki - who has been one of mentors and teachers in Professional Wrestling.
.
All of us sharing a lineage to Karl Gotch.
.
It ain't part time. It never has been.
.
It ain't a "hobby". It never was.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by "𝕿𝖍𝖊 𝖂𝖆𝖗𝖒𝖆𝖘𝖙𝖊𝖗" Josh Barnett in Los Angeles, California with @kingsroadmerch. May be an image of text.

node.text:
A big Congratulations to @pathsmith as he win the @usawrestling world team trials in Greco this weekend.
.
Pat did some of his camp with me, @bigtonynelson, @victorhenrymma and others up in Lake Arrowhead and his hard work has paid off well. Here's a little video of us drilling up there. 
.
Nice work Pat!
.
#Wrestling

I will have three new Catch Wrestling technique videos coming out soon from @bjj.fanatics. Here I get to sit down with @bernardofariabjj and show you guys some of what we filmed.
.
Enjoy!
.
Reposted from @bernardofariabjj Killer Grappling Achilles Lock by @joshlbarnett

node.text:
#tbt to winning the King of Pancrase title representing NJPW with my brothers Iizuka and Nakanishi in my corner. Enson Inoue was there with us too.
.
For me, I felt a lot pride to raise the flag of New Japan Pro Wrestling and for Pro Wrestling at large. Working and shooting - two sides of the same coin.
.
.
.
.
.
.
